{"tid":1887561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好尷尬點算好","createTime":"2020-02-19T15:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T17:15:57.000Z","uid":302802,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de2a67d5a7eeb478926d5ee93832e75ec4394972","tid":1887561,"uid":302802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"我個男仔frd就有條拍咗三年拖嘅女<br />\n兩個都諗過分手但傾掂數所以無事<br />\n但間唔中吹水嘅時侯都知條仔仲有分手念頭不過冇咁做 始終太耐<br />\n之後今年個frd識咗個新女仔<br />\n個frd仲主動係咁同個女仔傾計 日日wtsapp<br />\n勁多身體接觸 幾日就變得勁熟<br />\n我同個女仔都frd嘅 所以我都知大概發生咩事<br />\n兩個都鐘意對方不過就係我個frd有女所以先冇further嘅發展<br />\n點知俾我咁啱發現咗佢哋stage3咗仲差啲stage4<br />\n仲傾掂數話只要唔好俾人發現就會繼續keep住呢種關係<br />\n但我已經發現咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好尷尬 我應該點算<br />\n3個都係我嘅frd<br />\n唔知撐邊個好<br />\n唔知同唔同原本條女講好<br />\n唔知應唔應該cover新個條女好<br />\n定我應該由得佢哋算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32f427f65ff17352ae5ad8b2454e8164bdf1da5","tid":1887561,"uid":307927,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"男仔咁進取既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有佢一半勇敢都唔洗成日上連登9up"},{"pid":"b5535f822c3c51e421fd2c842fcd444bb20926e3","tid":1887561,"uid":131125,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:32:54.000Z","msg":"都已經唔care舊果個女朋友點諗又唔分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殘過地底泥"},{"pid":"c5286ea614bbee0a3dd21b86b021d1b5b7890d53","tid":1887561,"uid":302802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5535f822c3c51e421fd2c842fcd444bb20926e3","tid":1887561,"uid":131125,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:32:54.000Z","msg":"都已經唔care舊果個女朋友點諗又唔分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殘過地底泥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"本身諗住隻眼開隻眼閉就算<br />\n點知發現佢哋over哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e49514b5365bd047c8bf93d403